# This directory holds trained model .pkl files generated by running the pipeline.
# Models are excluded from git (see .gitignore) because they are large binary
# artifacts that are fully reproducible by running Page 3 (Train Models).
#
# To regenerate:
#   1. Run the Streamlit app: streamlit run app/Home.py
#   2. Upload datasets on Page 1
#   3. Run preprocessing on Page 2
#   4. Click "Train Models" on Page 3
